@ProviderService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5241
@BearerToken = <your-jwt-token-here>

### Health check (anonymous)
GET {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### ── Provider Profiles ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create provider profile (ServiceProvider role required)
POST {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessName": "AutoCare Pro",
  "description": "Professional car maintenance and repair services",
  "phoneNumber": "+212600000001",
  "address": "123 Rue Hassan II",
  "city": "Casablanca",
  "country": "Morocco"
}

###

### Get all active providers (any authenticated user)
GET {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get my profile (ServiceProvider role required)
GET {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/my
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get provider by id (any authenticated user)
GET {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Update provider profile (ServiceProvider role required)
PUT {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "businessName": "AutoCare Pro Updated",
  "city": "Rabat"
}

###

### Delete provider profile (ServiceProvider role required)
DELETE {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### ── Service Offerings ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Add a service offering
POST {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/services
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Oil Change",
  "description": "Full synthetic oil change with filter replacement",
  "price": 250.00,
  "durationMinutes": 45,
  "category": "Maintenance"
}

###

### Update a service offering
PUT {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 275.00,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Delete a service offering
DELETE {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/services/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### ── Availability ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get availability for a provider (any authenticated user)
GET {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Set availability slot (upsert by DayOfWeek)
PUT {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "08:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00",
  "isAvailable": true
}

###

### Delete an availability slot
DELETE {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/availability/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###

### ── Gallery ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Add gallery image
POST {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/gallery
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://storage.example.com/providers/shop-front.jpg",
  "caption": "Our workshop front view",
  "displayOrder": 0
}

###

### Delete gallery image
DELETE {{ProviderService_HostAddress}}/api/providers/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/gallery/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
Authorization: Bearer {{BearerToken}}

###
